{
  "text": "where cn i is the i-th basic color term, x encodes the present pixel whose RGB values are g(x), and p(cn i |g) is the probability of a color name computed by the mapping learned in [CITATION_1] . Afterwards, the CN descriptor of an image region R is defined as follows:",
